Package: cogplan9
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, inferno-kernel (>= 1.0)
Description: Plan9-based cognitive operating system
 CogPlan9 is an AGI-enabled extension of the Plan 9 operating system
 that integrates cognitive computing capabilities based on the OpenCog
 framework.
 .
 Key features:
  - Plan9 cognitive kernel extensions
  - 9P cognitive file servers
  - libatomspace (Plan9 native implementation)
  - libpln (Probabilistic Logic Networks)
  - Cognitive syscalls
  - MachSpace (distributed hypergraph)
  - Cognitive Fusion Reactor
  - ECAN (Economic Attention Network)
  - Integration with Inferno kernel

Package: cogplan9-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: cogplan9 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development files for CogPlan9
 Development headers, libraries, and tools for building applications
 on the CogPlan9 cognitive operating system.
